## THE THREE MOVES THAT MATTER MOST

If you only have **3 days**, do exactly these:

1. **Wire the geo-matching** (3 hours) — transforms placeholder into working core feature
2. **Add 15 unit tests + fix CI** (2 days) — largest single scoring jump
3. **Fix JWT secret + add NoSQL sanitization** (30 min) — closes the security gap

Everything else is optimization. These three changes move you from B+ to A.
